sp {mac*apply*move-mac-boat*record*last-operator*types*1
  (state <s> ^name mac
    ^operator <o>)
  (<o> ^name move-mac-boat
    ^bank <bank>
    ^{ << missionaries cannibals >> <type> } <n>
    ^types 1)
-->
